        "action": "Ban motor insurers from increasing premiums for non fault claims",
        "additional_details": "We feel this practice is unfair and affects thousands of people.",
        "background": "Ban the practice of insurers and underwriters being able to increase premiums after non-fault claims. We believe it is defamatory to accuse people of making non-fault claims as being at higher risk of claiming again.",
